title: TPB_AFK.(2013)-hd.1080p-h264-Remastered[)(]Ac3-5.1-(Sw+En)+(En-s
description:
Here is our third remastered version ,this time based on the Original mvk h.264
hd.1080p from Simon Klose.
Remastered as same format (mkv h264) but now to AC3-5.1/6-channels/48 Khz/16 Bit/512 Kbps

Result is very acceptable and sound has been sucessfully upmixed to 6 channels anyway.
Still more pleasant than only 2 channels so.

Spoken language : Swedish+English

SubTitle : English 

Final size : 8,04 Go (BD9 or DVD 8.5)
H264 here has been executed with NVidia CUDA.
